title: Plat5 cause inactivity, Dia 3 last season! Every role looking for a Ranked Team and play some gamez!
body:
I really want to play some serious teamrankeds, having fun ofc =)
Im german, but my english is good ( imo) 
I can play the role you guys need, and learn it even better.
I was dia 3 last season, didnt play much this season so i got ranked plat 1 , deranked to plat 5 cause i was inactiv.
If anyone has a spot, or wants to try and play, I would be happy to play with you guys!
Add me if you are intrested !
SweetLittlePanda ig
